{
  "stem": "13469.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All Jews in Holland had to live in Amsterdam, which, of course, was part of the overall plan, so that they could get us all together and pick us up easier.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had to move from Naarden.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think it was early in 1942 we moved to Amsterdam, like all Jews had to by that time, because many of them, or most of them, probably, lived in Amsterdam to start with.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Did you take all your possessions with you?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- we did, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] We never knew whether we took all our possessions from Berlin.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we took a lot, because we know that we had both an upright piano and a grand piano.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, in fact, the grand piano is in Naarden in this fortress.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We-- Before we went into the camps kind of thing, we gave all those things for safekeeping to lots of people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this grand piano, it was too big to go into the flat that we went to in Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we left it in Naarden, and we gave it to the church.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And after the war, we found that it was still in the church.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they asked whether we wanted it back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER] But we hadn't really got room for it, to take it with us to London [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My uncle had a grand piano already anyway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we left it in-- in Naarden.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And as far as I know, it's still in Naarden now, kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't suppose many people realize that it was ours, or my father's really.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So he was musical.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- and-- and they, and my uncle as well, they were very much into opera, and Wagner in particular, which is not the right sort of thing, but--",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
